desc: Online Store card shop specializing with cards from 1980s and 1990s. We sell all current product singles, sera, and boxes.

layout.text: Sports cards have been a hobby and past-time for dad and I. We have a lot of wonderful memories of opening packs, putting together sets, and discussing player stats. We always dreamed of opening a sports card store together, and now 20 years later I have pursued this dream in his memory..
